headline: FirstEnergy Grid Upgrade In Monmouth Tests Valuation And Earnings Outlook
summary: FirstEnergy subsidiary Jersey Central Power & Light is launching a major grid upgrade in northern Monmouth County as part of the long term Energize365 program. The project targets nearly 25,000 homes and businesses with modernized lines, new poles, and added redundancy to support more reliable service. This work is one piece of a planned multi year $28b capital investment across FirstEnergy's service territories. For investors tracking NYSE:FE, this Monmouth County project is a fresh,...
